snippet.title: Monster Jam Steel Titans - PC Gameplay (Steam)
snippet.description:
THQ Nordic and Rainbow Studios (of MX vs ATV fame) try their hand at a modern Monster Jam game. Did they succeed? You be the judge.

And yes, this really is a Bakugan Dragonoid monster truck, as it was a standalone DLC. And it's based on the actual Bakugan Monster Jam Truck toy from Spin Master.

Monster Jam Steel Titans game (C) THQ Nordic
Monster Jam (C) Feld Motor Sports, Inc.
Bakugan (C) Spin Master
Steam page: https://store.steampowered.com/app/824280/Monster_Jam_Steel_Titans/
